OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThursday's election could be
OL,8,F"Starmageddon" for the Prime Minister
OL,9,F` with SNP Westminster leader Stephen
OL,10,FFlynn claiming that while the Labour
OL,11,Fleader promised voters change he had
OL,12,F"only delivered chaos".
OL,14,FWith the SNP campaigning to win an
OL,15,Foverall majority at Holyrood, Mr Flynn
OL,16,Fsaid that Scottish Parliament election
OL,17,F"could spell curtains" for the Prime
OL,18,FMinister.
