OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FAs well as the Scottish elections,
OL,8,Fwhich could see Labour fall behind
OL,9,FReform UK at Holyrood, Sir Keir faces
OL,10,Fthe prospect of his party potentially
OL,11,Flosing power in Wales for the first
OL,12,Ftime in the history of devolution.
OL,14,FCouncil elections across England could
OL,15,Falso see Labour lose seats to both
OL,16,FReform UK and the Greens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
