OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FIn the midst of this there has been
OL,8,Frenewed speculation over Sir Keir's
OL,9,Fleadership of the party, with
OL,10,Fsuggestions that possible challengers
OL,11,Fto the PM, such as UK Health Secretary
OL,12,FWes Streeting, Greater Manchester
OL,13,FMayor Andy Burnham and former deputy
OL,14,Fprime minister Angela Rayner could be
OL,15,Fpreparing to move.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
