OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMr Flynn, who himself is running for
OL,8,FHolyrood on Thursday, has already
OL,9,Flikened the "political infighting" in
OL,10,Fthe Prime Minister's party to
OL,11,F"auditions for Labour Party Celebrity
OL,12,FTraitors".
OL,14,FBut nearly two year's on from Labour's
OL,15,F2024 Westminster election victory, he
OL,16,Fsaid the Holyrood vote was "the first
OL,17,Fopportunity for people in Scotland to
OL,18,Fhave their say" on Sir Keir's
OL,19,Fpremiership.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@bO]sD@AOUtD@IO]xD@\OUzD@OO]
