OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMr Flynn claimed: "The Scottish
OL,8,Felection could spell curtains for Keir
OL,9,FStarmer if enough people vote SNP to
OL,10,Ftackle the cost of living, improve our
OL,11,FNHS and secure a fresh start with
OL,12,Findependence.
OL,14,F"This is the cost-of-living election.
OL,16,F"At a time when families are being
OL,17,Fbattered by sky-high bills, it is
OL,18,Funforgiveable that the Labour Party is
OL,19,Fcompletely distracted by scandals and
OL,20,Finfighting and has failed to lift a
OL,21,Ffinger to help hard-pressed households.
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
