OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Voters were told things would get
OL,8,Fbetter but Brexit Britain is more
OL,9,Fbroken than ever.
OL,11,F"Under the Labour Party, energy bills
OL,12,Fwill soon be #700 higher than
OL,13,Fpromised, food and fuel prices have
OL,14,Fgone through the roof, UK unemployment
OL,15,Fis at a five-year high and families
OL,16,Fare struggling to get by."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
