OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe SNP Westminster leader blasted:
OL,8,F"It's no wonder that across Scotland,
OL,9,FWales and England people are talking
OL,10,Fabout this election being a
OL,11,FStarmageddon.
OL,13,F"On Thursday, Scotland can make Labour
OL,14,Flisten, prioritise the cost of living
OL,15,Fand secure that fresh start of
OL,16,Findependence by voting SNP."
OL,18,FScottish Labour deputy leader Jackie
OL,19,FBaillie said: "This election is about
OL,20,Fsending one person packing and that is
OL,21,FJohn Swinney.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUxD@\O]{D@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
