OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777943048
OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"With our NHS in crisis, our schools
OL,8,Fin chaos and crime rising in our
OL,9,Fcommunities, it's no wonder the SNP
OL,10,Fdon't want to talk about their record.
OL,12,F"The SNP is telling Scots their
OL,13,Fservices and their government don't
OL,14,Fmatter by insisting they should treat
OL,15,Fthis crucial election as a protest
OL,16,Fvote.
OL,18,F"The choice on Thursday is a simple
OL,19,Fone ` more of the same with the SNP or
OL,20,Fchange with Scottish Labour.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
