OL,3,CThursday's elections could be
OL,4,C'Starmageddon' for PM, Stephen Flynn
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"To reject Reform, beat the SNP and
OL,8,Fchange Scotland, vote Scottish Labour
OL,9,Fon May 7."
